  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Half Built: Casino</strong> is the Casino Tycoon game from Short Olive Games. Build your dream casino! Do it yourself or hire a crew of builders to help you out. Out now in EARLY ACCESS so you can test it out and watch it grow!<br> <br><u>Casino Floor</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your favorite games. Slots, Pokers, Craps, Blackjack, roulette, and more to come. Hire Dealers to help you succeed. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1907990/extras/0f018188609476e54726227d64f04de2.avif?t=1774114104\" width=800 height=376 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Services</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Provide services to your guests. Keep their stomachs full and their bladders empty. Hire servers to bring guests drinks to help increase bet size. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1907990/extras/4165a541658c2f3ab0cd46b95ee6d907.avif?t=1774114104\" width=128 height=188 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Keep it simple with some vending machines...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1907990/extras/b7c6f528f087e84e9e9cafc43cf5718a.avif?t=1774114104\" width=600 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or build a buffet! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1907990/extras/a67629e21f9c48562aee5f777aedb34d.avif?t=1774114104\" width=1134 height=699 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Mob and Loans</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take loans from the mob to keep growing but don't miss a payment! Miss too many payments and they will come after you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1907990/extras/bc5c4f9c6a75bc4e647d9f412b232e0d.avif?t=1774114104\" width=1184 height=838 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Entertainment</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire Entertainers. Street Performers will bring extra guests who will stick around and try their luck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1907990/extras/794c8a361c6569310bfa2ccf51d4b8b0.avif?t=1774114104\" width=148 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Cash and Theives</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Too much money on hand? Build a vault to keep it all stored. Watch out for thieves! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1907990/extras/ea5afeed786cb91047569ffc6f457027.avif?t=1774114104\" width=682 height=316 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Theives will always be looking for new ways to steal from you. Make sure to chase them off!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Technology and Research</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Research new items and unlock new options.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1907990/extras/db43515668106b1b1b6018d6a2cc7863.avif?t=1774114104\" width=800 height=468 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for taking a look at Half Built: Casino!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join us now in Early Access and watch the game grow and have your say on potential new content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world-class legitimate enterprise or a seedy backroom game room? The choice is yours with Half Built: Casino!</p>",
